{"tid":2117761,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【東方某某強国的語言】借問聲，乜撚野叫「回擊」？","createTime":"2020-07-21T05:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T05:57:01.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55cf15f52d189ffbace2529f59256fe4755b4300","tid":2117761,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"英國暫停執行與香港引渡協議 中方斥一錯再錯將作回擊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538983-20200721.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538983-20200721.htm&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=dca76fdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538983-20200721.htm&h=6000a9d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538983-20200721.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n英國宣布即時暫停執行與香港之間的引渡協議，並將香港納入武器禁運適用範圍。中國駐英大使館發言人批評，英方多次圍繞香港國安法做出錯誤言行，干涉香港事務和中國內政，中方已多次向英方提出嚴正交涉，表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，英方不顧中方嚴正立場與一再交涉，變本加厲，一錯再錯，對於干涉中國內政的行徑，中方必將作出堅決<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">回擊</span></strong></span>。中方又敦促英方不要在錯誤的道路上越走越遠，否則必將自食其果。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，英國外相藍韜文在國會表示，北京在香港實施《港區國安法》，違反《中英聯合聲明》及國際義務。在野工黨與部分執政保守黨議員都表示，期望英國政府進一步加大制裁力度。"},{"pid":"dcd5e0587061eb7872a2ca361185d6beaa607b93","tid":2117761,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:24:24.000Z","msg":"回應就回應<br />\n反擊就反擊<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野叫回擊？"},{"pid":"990a7bb9bf67331b87792acc66503e89d06608f7","tid":2117761,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc443b9e4b58baf0e211f00792f6866485399edd","tid":2117761,"uid":46587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://proxy.flss.edu.hk/~science/06/study_notes/1/lseb1_e.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproxy.flss.edu.hk%2F~science%2F06%2Fstudy_notes%2F1%2Flseb1_e.html&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=c9b8afd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://proxy.flss.edu.hk/~science/06/study_notes/1/lseb1_e.html</a><br />\n<br />\nNote: If the burner is lit without closing the air hole, <span class=\"red\">striking back (回擊) </span>will happen. The flame burns inside the chimney with a hissing sound. Striking back is dangerous. When it occurs, turn the gas tap off immediately and report to the teacher. The collar becomes very hot. Do not touch it.<br />\n<img src=\"https://kohyizhescienceeportfolio.files.wordpress.com/2011/08/strikeback.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkohyizhescienceeportfolio.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F08%2Fstrikeback.jpg&h=13ba0989&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cbc21ebd70462214852e152b2ed31a496724295","tid":2117761,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"990a7bb9bf67331b87792acc66503e89d06608f7","tid":2117761,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"日本動漫嘅角色招數竟然用於東方某某大国嘅官方外交辭令之上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6c0245c9497dc772f910bfedc0266e2ab68f7d","tid":2117761,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"反係禁字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}